# Git push (agents)

**Always** use:

```bash
python scripts/git_push.py
```

Release: `python scripts/git_push.py --ref vVERSION`

## On failure

Read **`=== GIT PUSH DIAGNOSTIC ===`**, apply **`recommended_fix`**, then re-run. Do not blind-retry `git push`.

See `reactwoo-geocore/docs/git-push-windows.md`.
